    Methods in com.app.validator.impl with parameters of type ClientDto
    Modifier and Type
    Method
    Description
    String
    ClientDtoValidator.validate(ClientDto client)
    Validates the given ClientDto object by checking the following: The name is provided and has the correct length and valid characters. The surname is provided and has the correct length and valid characters. The client's age is greater than or equal to the minimum allowed age. The client has sufficient cash (greater than the minimum required amount). If any of the validations fail, an appropriate error message is returned.
